          "date": "2015-05-17 17:24:55.000000000",
          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "LU-6602 llog: increase llog chunk size",
        "message": "LU-6602 llog: increase llog chunk size\n\nIncrease update llog chunk size from 8192 to 32768, so\none cross-MDT operation can includes more update records,\nand it can create striped directory with more stripe\ncount.\n\nAdding a LLOG_F_BIG_CHUNK flag in the llog header flag,\nif the llog file has such flag, then it means it will\nuse the bigger chunk size (32KB).\n\nAnd also remove a few padding in object_udpate_param,\nso we can pack more updates and parameters in one\nllog record (the maximum size is 32KB).\n\nSigned-off-by: wang di <di.wang@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ie598881524e990c84c82ef9b2fa31e3f864b0e50\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
